GRAPHIC DESIGNER

SUMMARY

Highly creative and multi-talented Graphic Designer with more than 14 years in multi-media and graphic design.
Highlights
Corporate design Advanced typography knowledge Strong design sense Conceptual thinker
Time management Creative and artistic Self-motivated professional Social Media Marketing

Graphic Designer
Company Name
— City , State

Work closely with clients from initial design to end product.

Owner - Graphic Artist
Company Name
— City , State
Manage and maintain a website and numerous social media sites.

Senior Graphic Designer
Company Name
— City , State

Worked closely with Federated's print shop and other local printing agencies.

Visual Communications
